| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1951 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 17c0b9ca-a2c0-5417-babd-8fd27b738ea4"
